properties.SQL Query:
CREATE TABLE userdata (
    userID bigint NOT NULL,
    name varchar(255),
    username varchar(255),
    email varchar(255),
    phone varchar(255),
    PRIMARY KEY (userID)
);

processGroups.name: Fetch Userdata and query address data

properties.address_data:
SELECT 
  id,
  address_address as street,
  address_city as city,
  address_state as state,
  address_postalCode as postalCode,
  address_country as country
FROM FLOWFILE

properties.contact_data:
SELECT 
  id,
  (RPATH_STRING(address, '/address')) as street,
  (RPATH_STRING(address, '/city')) as city,
  (RPATH_STRING(address, '/state')) as state,
  (RPATH_STRING(address, '/postalCode')) as postalCode,
  (RPATH_STRING(address, '/country')) as country
FROM FLOWFILE

properties.SQL Query:
CREATE TABLE address (
    id int NOT NULL,
    street varchar(255),
    postalCode varchar(255),
    city varchar(255),
    state varchar(255),
    country varchar(255),
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
